flowPara.flowSpan: Get familiar with research software development tools and practices (git and GitHub, AI tools for coding, reproducible enviroments, testing, containers, modular code development, documentation ...).

flowRoot.flowPara: Interactive 6 half-day event. You can join on your own, watch together with a team or join an in-person room (only some locations).
